satisfactory' improvement to the contribution from new or recently
modernised houses.
The outcome was also aided, he added, by an early Easter with sales in the
run-up to the holiday falling in the first half.
The interim dividend is raised 13 per cent, from 3p to 3.4p, payable from
earnings of 9.827p per share, compared with 8.975p.
